preference.name: CAE_persist_StructureMapLog
preference.preference_description: Controls whether a log is attached as a dataset to the root item revision of the created structure in a data map or a CAE Structure Map.This is an optional preference. Valid Values: 0 - No log is attached as a dataset to the root item revision. 1 - A log is attached as a dataset to the root item revision.
